{"tid":2070464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運輸署建議降低巴士加班門檻 企位每平方米減至4人","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T07:01:24.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aadbdbd3efd1f97780320837589a7228043d611c","tid":2070464,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"運輸署建議降低巴士加班門檻 企位每平方米減至4人<br />\n2020-06-19 HKT 13:17<br />\n<br />\n運輸署去年就專營巴士上可站立的乘客數目作檢討後，建議修訂行政指引，由每平方米可站立約6名乘客減至4人。<br />\n<br />\n在立法會交通事務委員會，署方表示，法例與海外地區的相關規定大致相若，並無需要修例，所以建議採取行政指引方式，為乘客提供更舒適的專營巴士服務，並同時建議降低現時增加巴士調配的門檻，在修訂指引後，只需要在最繁忙的半小時內載客率達90%，以及在 1小時內載客率達75%，專營巴士公司便需要增加車輛調配及班次。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532971-20200619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532971-20200619.htm&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5c42115e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532971-20200619.htm&h=10fc710b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532971-20200619.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c4392d41bb33f90bc801f565e5e3b4cbffe93752","tid":2070464,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"屌你 不如正視下鬼車呢個問題先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0b1f21db8e562bd8586998f188b0c6e8e1c415","tid":2070464,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4392d41bb33f90bc801f565e5e3b4cbffe93752","tid":2070464,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"屌你 不如正視下鬼車呢個問題先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"同埋教育下啲公路炸彈唔好亂Cut線導致偽塞車"}]}